lenders.name: brands
lenders.occupational_info:
The nLight is a revolutionary lighting control system that creates a mesh network of all your lighting controls to achieve a distributed intelligence. With nLight, you can enjoy a lighting control system that does not require centrally hardwired equipment and offers a web-based lighting management system instead. 
Acuity Brands’ Sensor Switch has designed nLight to integrate time-based lighting control with sensor-based lighting control for an intelligent mesh network. It enables zones of nLight devices to self-commission and function independently. This means an optimized operational and energy efficiency and a conveniently simple wireless light control system. 
With nLight’s lower overall equipment cost and maintenance as well as its easy plug-and-play installation, you can enjoy its benefits without delays or difficult retrofit transitions. It is also designed for flexible architecture and to easily accommodate expansions. If you’re looking for high precision lighting controls and unsurpassed energy efficiency, nLight can be the lighting control system for you.
